STM32F407

  1. version:1.7

  2. description:STM32F407

  3. cpu:
    name CM4
    revision r0p1
    endian little
    mpuPresent true
    fpuPresent true
    nvicPrioBits 4
    vendorSystickConfig false

  4. addressUnitBits:8

  5. width:32

  6. size:0x20

  7. resetValue:0x0

  8. resetMask:0xFFFFFFFF

  9. peripherals:

    1. RNG:

      Random number generator

      1. groupName : RNG

      2. baseAddress : 0x50060800

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x400 | usage=registers |

      4. interrupt :

        FPU:FPU interrupt value:81

      5. registers :

          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          RNDATA Random data 0 32

    6. DMA1:

      derivedFromDMA2

      1. baseAddress : 0x40026000

      2. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream0:DMA1 Stream0 global interrupt value:11

      3. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream1:DMA1 Stream1 global interrupt value:12

      4. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream2:DMA1 Stream2 global interrupt value:13

      5. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream3:DMA1 Stream3 global interrupt value:14

      6. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream4:DMA1 Stream4 global interrupt value:15

      7. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream5:DMA1 Stream5 global interrupt value:16

      8. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream6:DMA1 Stream6 global interrupt value:17

      9. interrupt :

        DMA1_Stream7:DMA1 Stream7 global interrupt value:47

    7. RCC:

      Reset and clock control

      1. groupName : RCC

      2. baseAddress : 0x40023800

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x400 | usage=registers |

      4. interrupt :

        RCC:RCC global interrupt value:5

      5. registers :

        1. CR
          (displayName:CR) : clock control register addressOffset: 0x0 size:0x20 access: resetValue: 0x00000083

          HSIRDY Internal high-speed clock ready flag 1 1
          HSION Internal high-speed clock enable 0 1

    73. OTG_HS_DEVICE:

      USB on the go high speed

      1. groupName : USB_OTG_HS

      2. baseAddress : 0x40040800

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x400 | usage=registers |

      4. registers :

        1. OTG_HS_DCFG
          (displayName:OTG_HS_DCFG) : OTG_HS device configuration register addressOffset: 0x0 size:32 access: read-write resetValue: 0x02200000
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          DSPD Device speed 0 2
          NZLSOHSK Nonzero-length status OUT handshake 2 1
          DAD Device address 4 7
          PFIVL Periodic (micro)frame interval 11 2
          PERSCHIVL Periodic scheduling interval 24 2
        2. OTG_HS_DCTL
          (displayName:OTG_HS_DCTL) : OTG_HS device control register addressOffset: 0x4 size:32 access: resetValue: 0x0
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          RWUSIG Remote wakeup signaling 0 1
          SDIS Soft disconnect 1 1
          GINSTS Global IN NAK status 2 1
          GONSTS Global OUT NAK status 3 1
          TCTL Test control 4 3
          SGINAK Set global IN NAK 7 1
          CGINAK Clear global IN NAK 8 1
          SGONAK Set global OUT NAK 9 1
          CGONAK Clear global OUT NAK 10 1
          POPRGDNE Power-on programming done 11 1
        3. OTG_HS_DSTS
          (displayName:OTG_HS_DSTS) : OTG_HS device status register addressOffset: 0x8 size:32 access: read-only resetValue: 0x00000010
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          SUSPSTS Suspend status 0 1
          ENUMSPD Enumerated speed 1 2

          FNSOF Frame number of the received SOF 8 14

    74. OTG_HS_PWRCLK:

      USB on the go high speed

      1. groupName : USB_OTG_HS

      2. baseAddress : 0x40040E00

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x3F200 | usage=registers |

      4. registers :

        1. OTG_HS_PCGCR
          (displayName:OTG_HS_PCGCR) : Power and clock gating control register addressOffset: 0x0 size:32 access: read-write resetValue: 0x0
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          STPPCLK Stop PHY clock 0 1
          GATEHCLK Gate HCLK 1 1
          PHYSUSP PHY suspended 4 1

    75. HASH:

      Hash processor

      1. groupName : HASH

      2. baseAddress : 0x50060400

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x400 | usage=registers |

      4. interrupt :

        HASH_RNG:Hash and Rng global interrupt value:80

      5. registers :

        1. CR
          (displayName:CR) : control register addressOffset: 0x0 size:0x20 access: resetValue: 0x00000000
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          INIT Initialize message digest calculation 2 1
          DMAE DMA enable 3 1
          DATATYPE Data type selection 4 2
          MODE Mode selection 6 1
          ALGO0 Algorithm selection 7 1
          NBW Number of words already pushed 8 4
          DINNE DIN not empty 12 1
          MDMAT Multiple DMA Transfers 13 1
          LKEY Long key selection 16 1
          ALGO1 ALGO 18 1
        2. DIN

          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width

        3. STR

          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width

        4. HR0

          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          H0 H0 0 32
        5. HR1

        6. HR2

    76. CRYP:

      Cryptographic processor

      1. groupName : CRYP

      2. baseAddress : 0x50060000

      3. addressBlock :

        offset=0x0 | size=0x400 | usage=registers |

      4. interrupt :

        CRYP:CRYP crypto global interrupt value:79

      5. registers :

        1. CR
          (displayName:CR) : control register addressOffset: 0x0 size:0x20 access: resetValue: 0x00000000
          Fields
          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
          ALGODIR Algorithm direction 2 1
          ALGOMODE0 Algorithm mode 3 3
          DATATYPE Data type selection 6 2
          KEYSIZE Key size selection (AES mode only) 8 2
          FFLUSH FIFO flush 14 1
          CRYPEN Cryptographic processor enable 15 1
          GCM_CCMPH GCM_CCMPH 16 2
          ALGOMODE3 ALGOMODE 19 1
        2. SR
          (displayName:SR) : status register addressOffset: 0x4 size:0x20 access: read-only resetValue: 0x00000003

          Name Description Bit Offset bit Width
